DAEMONLab grants You a commercial, non-exclusive, and worldwide license to use the XN.CORE software. This license is designed to support your professional operations while ensuring the technical integrity of the product.

2. AUTHORIZED PROFESSIONAL USE
Internal Operations: You may install and use the Software across your organization to support your business objectives.

